EU Seeks to Water Down Merkel’s Competitiveness Pact, Welt Says

-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 
2011-02-28T08:40:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/eu-seeks-to-water-down-merkel-s-competitiveness-pact-welt-says.html
European Union officials plan to
discuss ways to water down Chancellor  Angela Merkel ’s proposals
to boost  Europe ’s competitiveness, German newspaper  Die Welt
reported , without saying how it got the information.  The proposals would make the changes sought by Germany and
France more flexible, including by allowing countries to keep
indexing wages to inflation, the newspaper reported on its
website. EU government negotiators plan to consider the measures
at a meeting in Brussels today, the report said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tony Czuczka in Berlin at 
 aczuczka@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at   jhertling@bloomberg.net  